race.description: Road To Magic Millions Book Now Handicap
race.comment: RICH MINX (1) couldn't have been more impressive saluting by six lengths on the Gold Coast last time out and will have derived a bunch of confidence from that dominant victory. Gets 3kg off with the claim and can go right on with the job now. MOULIN MISS (9) is one from one over this course and distance and will be ready to peak now third run back from a break. Has to be included. DETRIMENTAL (6) has a handy first-up record and may run a race while fresh. ACAPPELLA SUN (3) gets the Gollan/Lang combination and now finds the inside alley after scratchings. Cannot be underestimated. DEVINE FORCE (11) best of the rest.
